Detailed Description

template<class T>
class Util::Queable< T >

Base class of object queueable into double linked list.

To be en(de)queueable in a a Queue, a cell must be instance of a class derived from class Queable. A queueable cell may be in at most one queue. A queueable class must be declared as follow : 

    class X : public Queable<X> {
      ..; members etc...
    };
See also:
